    'hero.subtitle': 'From grain to glass — the art of fermentation,<br/>backed by science',
    'hero.btnPrograms': 'Study programmes',
    'hero.btnMore': 'Learn more',
    'hero.stat1': 'Years of NUFT tradition',
    'hero.stat2': 'University students',
    'hero.stat3': 'Degree levels',
    'hero.scroll': 'Scroll down',
    'about.tag': 'About the department',
    'about.title': 'Where science meets <em>the art of fermentation</em>',
    'about.lead': 'The Department of Biotechnology of Fermentation and Winemaking trains specialists in the field of knowledge 18 «Production and Technologies», specialty 181 «Food Technologies».',
    'about.p1': 'Training is provided at bachelor level (EP «Food Technologies and Engineering»), master level (EP «Technologies of Fermentation and Winemaking Products») and PhD level (EP «Food Technologies») in full-time and part-time modes.',
    'about.p2': 'The department was one of the first at the university to introduce and continues to offer <strong>dual education</strong>. Every year, 1–2 students study at the University of Geisenheim (Germany) under the <strong>Erasmus+</strong> programme in «Wine Technology».',
    'about.p3': 'The department\'s creed is <em>training future leaders</em>. We strive to unlock and develop our students\' potential so they gain the competences to tackle complex challenges and achieve personal success and financial independence.',
    'about.p4': 'Teaching is delivered by a highly qualified team: <strong>3 professors (Doctors of Technical Sciences)</strong> and <strong>10 associate professors (Candidates of Technical Sciences)</strong>.',
    'about.p5': 'The department runs a unique <strong>certificate programme «Sommelier profession and scientific-practical foundations of wine and spirits tasting»</strong>.',
    'about.p6': 'Students gain professional skills during placements at enterprises such as Obolon, Nemiroff, SAN InBev Ukraine, SHABO Wine Culture Centre, Koblevo, Mykulyntskyi Brewery, VARVAR microbrewery and others.',
    'about.downloadsTitle': 'Department presentation',
    'about.downloadsDesc': 'Download a short overview of the department for prospective students.',
    'about.btnUa': 'Download (UA)',
    'about.btnEn': 'Download (EN)',
    'about.feature1': 'Research',
    'about.feature1Text': 'Modern laboratories for microbial synthesis, fermentation and food-industry nanotechnology research.',
    'about.feature2': 'Industry placements',
    'about.feature2Text': 'Partnerships with craft breweries, wineries and fermented-beverage producers across Ukraine.',
    'about.feature3': 'International activity',
    'about.feature3Text': 'Exchange programmes, international conferences and cooperation with European universities and research centres.',
    'about.feature4': 'Three degree levels',
    'about.feature4Text': 'Bachelor\'s, Master\'s and PhD — a full cycle from fundamentals to dissertation.',
    'marquee.brewing': 'Brewing',
    'marquee.winemaking': 'Winemaking',
    'marquee.biotech': 'Biotechnology',
