    'programs.detail1_intro': 'The educational programme trains specialists who possess a set of specialist knowledge and are able to apply:',
    'programs.detail1_c1': 'fundamental concepts and principles of designing and operating food industry enterprises of various capacities and profiles, including craft food production;',
    'programs.detail1_c2': 'principles of developing new and improving existing food technologies;',
    'programs.detail1_c3': 'patterns governing the technological processes of food production;',
    'programs.detail1_c4': 'systems for calculating production needs in materials, financial and labour resources;',
    'programs.detail1_c5': 'basic principles of food quality and safety management systems;',
