    'programs.detail1_extra': 'The programme trains a versatile bachelor with fundamental and professionally-oriented knowledge across all branches of the food industry. It includes theoretical and practical training, dual education elements, international academic mobility (Erasmus+ at universities in Germany and Poland) and a wide selection of industrial placements.',
    'programs.detail1_careers': '<strong>Possible positions:</strong> enterprise director, chief technologist, production manager, food quality control engineer, workshop supervisor, laboratory manager.',
    'programs.detail2_intro': 'The BPBV Department is the only one in Ukraine covering all professional fields of the fermentation industry. The programme trains masters with fundamental and professionally-oriented knowledge capable of solving complex scientific and technical problems.',
