    'life.tag': 'Student life',
    'life.title': 'Learning through <em>experience</em>',
    'life.partnersTitle': 'Our industry partners',
    'life.t1Date': 'November 2024',
    'life.t1Title': 'Masterclass at VARVAR brewery',
    'life.t1Text': 'Bachelor and master students visited the VARVAR brewery, where chief technologist Olena Deryi gave a lecture and tour. Students saw the full technological cycle — from raw material preparation to the finished product — and took part in an educational tasting.',
    'life.t2Date': '2024',
    'life.t2Title': 'Intellectual property lecture from UkrNOIVI',
    'life.t2Text': 'Master\'s students joined a professional lecture from the Academy of Intellectual Property on «Intellectual property in the modern world» as part of the educational component under guarantor V. Prybylskyi.',
    'life.t3Date': 'October 2023',
    'life.t3Title': 'Visit to BEERMASTER BREWERY',
    'life.t3Text': 'Third-year students together with Assoc. Prof. Roman Mukoid visited the craft brewery at Respublica mall. Chief technologist Oleksandr Rudenko — a BPBV graduate — gave a detailed tour and educational tasting of malt, hops and various beer styles.',
    'life.t4Date': 'October 2023',
    'life.t4Title': 'Introduction to kombucha technology',
    'life.t4Text': 'First-year students visited the Eat Easy company, where department graduates Yevhen Khomets (Production Director) and Nazar Kosikovskyi (Chief Technologist) introduced them to the full kombucha production cycle and laboratory work.',
    'life.t5Date': 'October 2023',
    'life.t5Title': 'Open lecture on intellectual property',
    'life.t5Text': 'Assoc. Prof. Mykola Bondar gave an open class on «Intellectual and Industrial Property» for Master\'s students of the BTEC faculty on the topic: Intellectual property law in Ukraine.',
    'life.t6Date': '2023–2024',
    'life.t6Title': 'More events and excursions',
    'life.t6Text': 'Department students regularly visit production sites, take part in scientific conferences, tastings and masterclasses, gaining practical experience in real-world conditions.',
    'life.t2bDate': '29 September 2024',
    'life.t2bTitle': 'Lecture «From region to market» — geographical indications',
    'life.t2bText': 'With support from Prof. Vitalii Prybylskyi, a lecture was held on «From region to market: geographical indications as a tool for promoting Ukrainian goods» within the «IP Connecting Students» project.',
    'life.tSommelierDate': '2025',
    'life.tSommelierTitle': 'Visit to the final of «Ukraine\'s Best Sommelier 2025»',
    'life.tSommelierText': 'At the invitation of master\'s student Ivan Bachurin, department representatives Maryna Bilko and Roman Mukoid attended the competition final. The event brought together professionals from various fields.',
    'life.tParisDate': 'Paris 2025',
    'life.tParisTitle': 'Young wine tasters\' competition at Salon International De L\'Agriculture',
    'life.tParisText': 'Students Vladyslav Mylnykov and Mariia Lytovchenko represented Ukraine at the international competition in Paris. The delegation was led by Prof. Maryna Bilko.',
    'life.tNapoiDate': '2024–2025',
    'life.tNapoiTitle': 'Business meeting «Beverages of Ukraine. Tea and coffee»',
    'life.tNapoiText': 'NUFT lecturers took part in the business meeting. Assoc. Prof. Roman Mukoid moderated the discussion panel.',
    'life.tMarulloDate': '2024',
    'life.tMarulloTitle': 'Guest lecture by PhD Philip Marullo (Biolaffort, ISVV Bordeaux)',
    'life.tMarulloText': 'Lecture within the joint project of UkrWineIndustry and NUFT. The topic was innovative microbiological approaches in white wine production.',
    'life.tVarvar3Date': '2024',
    'life.tVarvar3Title': 'Third-year students at Varvar brewery',
    'life.tVarvar3Text': 'Third-year students and curator Roman Mukoid visited the Varvar brewery. The tour was led by chief brewer Anton Palamarchuk and chief technologist Olena Deryi.',
    'life.tNemiroff3Date': '8 April 2024',
    'life.tNemiroff3Title': 'Third-year students meet Nemiroff representatives',
    'life.tNemiroff3Text': 'The department hosted a meeting of third-year students with representatives of Nemiroff (LVN LIMITED LLC). Agreements were reached on internships and employment.',
    'life.tChervonoDate': '4 April 2024',
    'life.tChervonoTitle': 'Excursion to Chervonoslobidskyi distillery',
    'life.tChervonoText': 'Third-year students visited the Chervonoslobidskyi distillery state enterprise. The tour was guided by department graduate Ivan Dmytrovych Balokha.',
    'life.tNemiroff2Date': '2024',
    'life.tNemiroff2Title': 'Second-year students meet Nemiroff',
    'life.tNemiroff2Text': 'The department organized a meeting of second-year students with Nemiroff representatives. The company is ready to offer internship opportunities.',
    'life.tOPPDate': '24 January 2024',
    'life.tOPPTitle': 'Educational programme working group session',
    'life.tOPPText': 'Programme guarantor Prof. Vitalii Prybylskyi familiarized participants with the requirements for drafting the new edition of the educational programme.',
    'life.tVashchukDate': '30 October 2023',
    'life.tVashchukTitle': 'Guest lecture by Viktor Vashchuk (Silpo private breweries)',
    'life.tVashchukText': 'Assoc. Prof. Roman Mukoid invited Viktor Vashchuk, project lead of «Silpo private breweries». Topic: «Current state and prospects of beer production in Ukraine and worldwide».',
    'life.tVarvar17Date': '17 October 2023',
    'life.tVarvar17Title': 'Visit to Varvar brewery mini-brewery (year 3)',
    'life.tVarvar17Text': 'Students of groups TB-3-8 and TB-3-9sk visited the Varvar mini-brewery. The tour was led by chief microbiologist Olena Derii.',
    'life.tBeer1Date': '2023',
    'life.tBeer1Title': 'First-years at BeerMaster brewery',
    'life.tBeer1Text': 'First-year students together with Assoc. Prof. Mykola Bondar visited BeerMaster brewery. The tour was led by chief technologist Oleksandr Rudenko.',
